high_descs: Go forward toward the door, then turn right and go ahead to the coffee maker, above the dishwasher.
Pick up the mug at the coffee maker.
Go to the sink to your right.
Put the mug in the sink.
Pick up the spoon from in the sink.
Put the spoon in the mug.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug in the sink with a spoon in it.

high_descs: move forward and turn to the right at the counter and move to the coffee machine that is on the counter to the left of the sink
pick up the coffee mug that is on the coffee machine
move to the right to face the sink
put the coffee mug in to the sink
pick up the spoon that is in the sink
put the spoon into the the coffee mug that is in the sink with the handle down in to the mug
anns.task_desc: put a spoon in to a coffee mug in the sink

high_descs: Walk forward to the nearby door on the left, then turn right and walk across the room to the coffee machine by the sink.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Turn right and walk slightly forward to the sink.
Put the mug in the sink basin.
Pick up the spoon from the sink basin.
Put the spoon in the mug.
